          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <placeName>Louisville, Ky.</placeName>
                                        <date>August 15<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1850</date>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">Revd Sir,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">We are desirous of<lb/> procuring the Services of
                                        the <persName>Revd H. H. Henry</persName><lb/> (now minister
                                        of K. K. Benai Jeshurun<lb/> of
                                                  <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName>) as Professor of
                                        our Jewish<lb/> School in this City. Some Persons have<lb/>
                                        from Motives unknown to us spoken dispara<lb/>gingly of
                                        himâ€”and in addition to the<lb/> documents of unexceptionable
                                        Character from<lb/> the old Country, we are anxious to
                                        have<lb/> further proof to protect this Gentlemen, and<lb/>
                                        he has referred us to you. We shall<lb/> therefore feel
                                        particularly obliged if you<lb/> will favor us by Return as
                                        to the Character,<lb/> Talents &amp; Qualifications of this
                                        Gentlemen</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">We remain Revd Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(4)">Yours</p>
                              <p rend="indent(5)">obedient</p>
                              <p rend="indent(4)">
                                        <persName role="author">C. Lichten</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(4)">
                                        <persName role="author">E. Bamberger</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(4)"><persName role="author">L.
                                        Silberman</persName>.</p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p>To the</p>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
                              </p>
